'''Pirate Queen''',<ref name="Smuggler's Guide" /> or '''pirate queen''',<ref name="Takodana">{{Databank|takodana|Takodana}}</ref> was a title held by a [[pirate]].<ref name="Smuggler's Guide" /> [[Maz Kanata]] was also recognized as a pirate queen by many individuals including [[Tjepo Juibop]],<ref name="Pirate's Price" /> and her [[Takodana Castle|castle's]] rules were greatly respected by all due to this status.<ref name="Takodana" />

